text: Maria Mollestad (born 1992) is a Norwegian windsurfer. She qualified for competing at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Bærum Category:Norwegian windsurfers Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – RS:X Category:Olympic sailors of Norway
